 alt="DSC00714" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00714_thumb.jpg" width="464" height="174" /></a>     <br /><img title="DSC00709" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00709" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00709_2.jpg" width="154" height="104" /><img title="DSC00711" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00711" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00711_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" /><a href="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00726.jpg"><img title="DSC00726" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00726" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00726_thumb.jpg" width="154" height="104" /></a>    <br /><img title="DSC00719" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00719" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00719_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" /><img title="DSC00734" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00734" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00734_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" /><img title="DSC00729" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00729" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00729_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" />    <br /><img title="DSC00723" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00723" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00723_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" /><img title="DSC00736" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00736" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00736_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" /><img title="DSC00720" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00720" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00720_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" />    <br /><img title="DSC00733" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00733" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00733_1.jpg" width="154" height="101" /><img title="DSC00724" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00724" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00724_1.jpg" width="154" height="102" /><img title="DSC00730" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00730" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00730_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" />    <br /><img title="DSC00746" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00746" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00746_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" /><img title="DSC00745" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00745" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00745_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" /><img title="DSC00731" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00731" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/35b5755b7fde_12434/DSC00731_1.jpg" width="154" height="104" />    <br /><a href="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/ccc0a58c7ba8_7989/DSC00751.jpg"><img title="DSC00751" style="border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00751" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/ccc0a58c7ba8_7989/DSC00751_thumb.jpg" width="154" height="103" /></a><a href="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/ccc0a58c7ba8_7989/DSC00750.jpg"><img title="DSC00750" style="border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00750" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/ccc0a58c7ba8_7989/DSC00750_thumb.jpg" width="154" height="103" /></a><a href="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/ccc0a58c7ba8_7989/DSC00755.jpg"><img title="DSC00755" style="border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00755" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/ccc0a58c7ba8_7989/DSC00755_thumb.jpg" width="154" height="104" /></a></p>  <p>パンケーキクッションが完成し、完成の喜びと共に６人の女性が集まって、寛ぎながらあれやこれやと会話をしている時だった、私たち「イストモ」やなぁ…って、参加者のとんちゃんが突然言い出して、それで６人の椅子に座るイストモ記念写真を撮影するコトになった。確かに「まちのえんがわ」ワークショップの縁で、それもこの椅子の縁で集ったひとたちで、しかも、この日造った兄弟姉妹のようなパンケーキスツールたちは、それぞれの暮らしの中に置かれたりするわけで、そういう繋がりっていうのも、なんか凄くエエなぁ…とおもえるワークショップだった。    <br />    <br /><img style="float: none; margin-left: auto; display: block; margin-right: auto" src="https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/t31.0-8/11415593_855829681136791_7039968599452547910_o.jpg" width="349" height="465" /></p>  <p>経験を共有することが、コミュニケーションをスムーズにするのだとよく言われるが、確かに旅行とか、ワークショップとか、ま、それで、「記念撮影」なんかをすることで、その共有経験も焼き付けられたりするのかね…。</p>]]></description>
