play: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00067" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/16c5a2b5bd7b_73DB/DSC00067_thumb.jpg" width="117" height="174" /></a><a href="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/16c5a2b5bd7b_73DB/DSC00069.jpg"><img title="DSC00069" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00069" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/16c5a2b5bd7b_73DB/DSC00069_thumb.jpg" width="117" height="174" /></a><a href="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/16c5a2b5bd7b_73DB/DSC00073.jpg"><img title="DSC00073" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00073" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/16c5a2b5bd7b_73DB/DSC00073_thumb.jpg" width="117" height="174" /></a><a href="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/16c5a2b5bd7b_73DB/DSC00089.jpg"><img title="DSC00089" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; display: inline; padding-right: 0px; border-top-width: 0px" border="0" alt="DSC00089" src="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/16c5a2b5bd7b_73DB/DSC00089_thumb.jpg" width="117" height="174" /></a></p>  <p><font face="CenturyOldst">そうそう、土曜日の夕方に「まちのえんがわ」の前の道に佇むと、丸くて赤くて大きな夕日が、私の足をこんなに長～く伸ばしてくれて、きっと、春がやってきた気分を助長してくれたのだとおもう…。</font></p>  <p><a href="http://www.kimuko.net/blog/Windows-Live-Writer/f41da2469f96_14319/IMG_7054.jpg"><font face="CenturyOldst"><img title="IMG_7054" style="border-left-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; background-image: none; border-bottom-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-left: